Structure of the repository :
================================

graphe3d   	   	   	   		: main directory of the project
|-- ant 	  	  	  		: main directory of Ant
| 	|-- bin 	  	  		: contains launcher scripts
| 	|-- build.xml 	  		: file build.xml
| 	|-- etc 	  	  		: contains xsl goodies
| 	`-- lib 	  	  		: contains Ant jars and others libraries (ant, jdepend, javancss, junit)
|
|-- build 	  	  	  		: the build directory
| 	|-- class	  	  		: contains bytecode
|	|-- jar					: contains the API jar and the editor jar
| 	`-- web 	  	  		
| 	  	|-- api 	  		: contains documentation of the API (javadoc)
| 	  	|-- controle 	  	: contains mesures reports
| 	  	| 	|-- jdepend 	: contains jdepend report
| 	  	| 	`-- javancss 	: contains javancss report
| 	  	|-- index.html 		: file index.html
| 	  	|-- style 	  		: contains CSS styles
| 	  	`-- test 	  		: contains tests reports
|
|-- docs 	  	  	  		: contains documentation
|	|-- pdf 	  			: contains reports of conception
|	`-- uml 	  	  	  	: contains UML diagrams
|
|-- src 	  	  	  		: contains Java files and Tests files.
|-- ww 	  	  	  			: working directory
|-- xml						: contains the XML schema and an example of XML document.
`-- readme 	  	  			: file readme


Configuration of ant (UNIX):
============================

The following sets up the environment :
export ANT_HOME=~/workspace/graphe3d/ant (bash)
setenv ANT_HOME ~/workspace/graphe3d/ant (tcsh)

